quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  23,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  23,1,yaqeenan Falah payi hai imaan walon ne jo :
  23,2,apni namaz mein Khashoo ikhtiyar karte hain
  23,3,lughwiyaat se daur rehtay hain
  23,4,zkoh ke tareeqay par Amel hotay hain
  23,5,apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  23,6,siwaye apni biwion ke aur un aurton ke jo un ki malik Yamin mein hon ke un par ( mehfooz nah rakhnay mein ) woh qabil malamat nahi hain
  23,7,Albata jo uss ke ilawa kuch aur chahain wohi zayad-ti karne walay hain
  23,8,apni amanaton aur apne ehad o Paiman ka paas rakhtay hain
  23,9,aur apni namazon ki muhafizat karte hain
  23,10,yahi log woh waris hain
  23,11,jo meeras mein Firdous payen ge aur is mein hamesha rahen ge
  23,12,hum ne ensaan ko matti ke sat se banaya
  23,13,phir usay aik mehfooz jagah tapki hui boond mein tabdeel kya
  23,14,"phir is boond ko lothray ki shakal di, phir lothray ko booti bana diya, phir booti ki haddiyan banayen, phir hadion par gosht charhaya, phir usay aik doosri hi makhlooq bana khara kya"
  23,15,"pas bara hi babarkat hai Allah , sab karigron se acha karigar"
  23,16,"phir is ke baad tum ko zaroor marna hai, phir qayamat ke roz yaqeenan tum uthaye jao ge"
  23,17,"aur tumahray oopar hum ne saat rastay banaye, takhleeq ke kaam se hum kuch nabld nah thay"
  23,18,aur aasman se hum ne theek hisaab ke mutabiq aik khaas miqdaar mein pani utaara aur is ko zameen meintehra diya hum ussay jis terhan chahain gayab kar satke hain
  23,19,"phir is pani ke zareya se hum ne tumahray liye khajoor aur angoor ke baagh peda kar diye, tumahray liye un baghoon mein bohat se lazeez phal hain aur un se tum rozi haasil karte ho"
  23,20,"aur woh darakht bhi hum ne peda kya jo tor sinaa se nikalta hai, tail bhi liye hue ugta hai aur khanay walon ke liye saalan bhi"
  23,21,"aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumahray liye maweshion mein bhi aik sabaq hai un ke paiton mein jo kuch hai isi mein se aik cheez hum tumhe pilate hain, aur tumahray liye un mein bohat se dosray doosray faiday bhi hain"
  23,22,unn ko tum khatay ho aur unn par aur kashtiyon par sawaar bhi kiye jatay ho
  23,23,"hum ne Nooh ko is ki qoum ki taraf bheja is ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, is ke siwa tumahray liye koi aur mabood nahi hai, kya tum drtay nahi ho? """
  23,24,"is ki qoum ke jin sardaro ne maan-ne se inkaar kya woh kehnay lagey ke"" yeh shakhs kuch nahi hai magar aik bashar tum hi jaissa iss ki gharz yeh hai ke tum par bartari haasil kere Allah ko agar bhejna hota to farishtay bhejta yeh baat to hum ne kabhi apne baap dada ke waqton mein suni hi nahi ( ke bashar rasool ban kar aeye )"
  23,25,"kuch nahi, bas is aadmi ko zara junoon la-haq ho gaya hai kuch muddat aur dekh lau ( shayad afaqa ho jaye ) """
  23,26,"Nooh ne kaha"" parvar-digaar, un logon ne jo meri tkzib ki hai is par ab to hi meri madad farma """
  23,27,"hum ne is par wahi ki ke"" hamari nigrani mein aur hamari wahi ke mutabiq kashti tayyar kar phir jab hamara hukum aa jaye aur tanoor ubal parre to har qisam ke janwaron mein se aik aik jora le kar is mein sawaar ho ja, aur apne ahal o Ayal ko bhi sath le siwaye unn ke jin ke khilaaf pehlay hi faisla ho chuka hai, aur zaalmon ke maamla mein mujh se kuch nah kehna, yeh ab ghark honay walay hain"
  23,28,"phir jab to apne sathiyon sameit kashti par sawaar ho jaye to keh, shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hamein zalim logon se nijaat di"
  23,29,"aur keh, parvar-digaar, mujh ko barket wali jagah utaar aur too behtareen jagah dainay wala hai """
  23,30,iss qissay mein barri nishanain hain aur azmaish to hum kar ke hi rehtay hain
  23,31,un ke baad hum ne aik dosray doori ki qoum uthai
  23,32,"phir unn mein khud unhi ki qoum ka aik rasool bheja ( jis ne inhen dawat di ) ke Allah ki bandagi karo, tumahray liye uss ke siwa koi aur mabood nahi hai, kya tum drtay nahi ho ?"
  23,33,"uss ki qoum ke jin sardaro ne maan-ne se inkaar kya aur akhirat ki paishi ko jhatlaya, jin ko hum ne duniya ki zindagi mein aasooda kar rakha tha, woh kehnay lagey"" yeh shakhs kuch nahi hai magar aik bashar tum hi jaissa jo kuch tum khatay ho wohi yeh khata hai aur jo kuch tum peetay ho wohi yeh peeta hai"
  23,34,ab agar tum ne apne hi jaisay aik bashar ki itaat qubool kar li to tum ghatay hi mein rahay
  23,35,yeh tumhe ittila deta hai ke jab tum mar kar matti ho jao ge aur hadion ka panjar ban kar reh jao ge uss waqt tum ( qabron se ) nikalay jao ge ?
  23,36,"baeed, bilkul baeed hai yeh wada jo tum se kya ja raha hai"
  23,37,zindagi kuch nahi hai magar bas yahi duniya ki zindagi yahin hum ko marna aur jeena hai aur hum hargiz uthaye jaane walay nahi hain
  23,38,"yeh shakhs khuda ke naam par mehez jhoot ghurr raha hai aur hum kabhi is ki maan-ne walay nahi hain """
  23,39,"rasool ne kaha"" parvar-digaar, inn logon ne jo meri tkzib ki hai, is par ab to hi meri nusrat farma """
  23,40,"jawab mein irshad howa"" qareeb hai woh waqt jab yeh apne kiye par puchtain ge """
  23,41,aakhir kaar theek theek haq ke mutabiq aik hungama azeem ne un ko aa liya aur hum ne un ko kachra bana kar pheink diya door ho zalim qoum !
  23,42,phir hum ne un ke baad doosri qoumain uthayen
  23,43,koi qoum nah apne waqt se pehlay khatam hui aur nah is ke baad tehr saki
  23,44,"phir hum ne pay Dur pay apne rasool beje jis qoum ke paas bhi is ka rasool aaya, is ne ussay jhatlaya, aur hum aik ke baad aik qoum ko halaak karte chalay gay hatta ke un ko bas afsana hi bana kar chorra phatkaar unn logon par jo imaan nahi laatay !"
  23,45,phir hum ne moose aur is ke bhai haroon ko apni nishanion aur khuli sanad ke sath firaon aur is ke a'yane saltanat ki taraf bheja
  23,46,magar unhon ne taqqabur kya aur barri dun ki li
  23,47,"kehnay lagey"" kya hum apne hi jaisay do admion par imaan le ayen? aur aadmi bhi woh jin ki qoum hamari bandi hai """
  23,48,pas unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya aur halaak honay walon mein ja miley
  23,49,aur moose ko hum ne kitaab ataa farmai taakay log is se rahnumai haasil karen
  23,50,aur Ibn maryam aur is ki maa ko hum ne aik nishaan banaya aur un ko aik satah murtafa par rakha jo itminan ki jagah thi aur chashmay is mein jari thay
  23,51,"ae peghambro, khao pak cheeze aur amal karo Saleh , tum jo kuch bhi karte ho, mein is ko khoob jaanta hon"
  23,52,"aur yeh tumhari ummat aik hi ummat hai aur mein tumhara rab hon, pas mujhi se tum daro"
  23,53,magar baad mein logon ne apne deen ko aapas mein tukre tukre kar liya har giroh ke paas jo kuch hai usi mein woh magan hai
  23,54,"acha, to chhorro inhen, doobe rahen apni ghaflat mein aik waqt khaas taq"
  23,55,kya yeh samajte hain ke hum jo inhen maal o aulaad se madad diye ja rahay hain
  23,56,"to goya inhen bhalaiyan dainay mein sargaram hain? nahi, asal muamlay ka inhen shaoor nahi hai"
  23,57,jo apne rab ke khauf se daray rehtay hain
  23,58,jo apne rab ki ayaat par imaan laatay hain
  23,59,jo apne rab ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karte
  23,60,aur jin ka haal yeh hai ke dete hain jo kuch bhi dete hain aur dil unn ke is khayaal se kanpate rehtay hain ke hamein apne rab ki taraf palatna hai
  23,61,bhulaiyon ki taraf dornay walay aur Sabqat kar ke inhen pa lainay walay to dar haqeeqat yeh log hain
  23,62,"hum kisi shakhs ko is ki mqdrt se ziyada ki takleef nahi dete aur hamaray paas aik kitaab hai jo ( har aik ka haal ) theek theek bta dainay wali hai, aur logon par zulm behar haal nahi kya jaye ga"
  23,63,magar yeh log is muamlay se be khabar hain aur un ke aamaal bhi is tareeqay se ( jis ka oopar zikar kiya gaya hai ) mukhtalif hain woh apne yeh kartoot kiye chalay jayen ge
  23,64,yahan taq ke jab hum un ke ayyashon ko azaab mein pakar len ge to phir woh dakrana shuru kar den ge
  23,65,"ab band karo apni faryaad o fugaah, hamari taraf se ab koi madad tumhe nahi milni"
  23,66,meri ayaat sunai jati theen to tum ( rasool ki aawaz suntay hi ) ultay paon bhaag nikaltay thay
  23,67,apne ghamand mein uss ko khatir hi mein nah laatay thay apni chopalon mein uss par baatein chant-tay aur bakwaas kya karte thay
  23,68,to kya inn logon ne kabhi iss kalaam par ghhor nahi kya? ya woh koi aisi baat laya hai jo kabhi un ke islaaf ke paas nah aayi thi ?
  23,69,ya yeh apne rasool se kabhi ke waaqif nah thay ke ( aَn jana aadmi honay ke baais ) uss se bidaktayhain ?
  23,70,"ya yeh is baat ke qaail hain ke woh Majnoon hai? nahi, balkay woh haq laya hai aur haq hi un ki aksariyat ko nagawaar hai"
  23,71,"aur haq agar kahin inn ki khwahisaat ke peechay chalta to zameen aur aasman aur un ki saari abadi ka nizaam darham barham ho jata nahi, balkay hum un ka apna hi zikar unn ke paas laaye hain aur woh apne zikar se mun mourr rahay hain"
  23,72,kya too un se kuch maang raha hai? tairay liye tairay rab ka diya hi behtar hai aur woh behtareen Razaq hai
  23,73,"Tu , tuun ko sidhayrastay ki taraf bulaa raha hai"
  23,74,magar jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay woh raah e raast se hatt kar chalna chahtay hain
  23,75,agar hum inn par reham karen aur woh takleef jis mein aaj kal yeh mubtala hain door kar den to yeh apni sar kashi mein bilkul hi behak jayen ge
  23,76,"inn ka haal to yeh hai ke hum ne inhen takleef mein mubtala kya, phir bhi yeh apne rab ke agay nah jhuke aur nah aajzi ikhtiyar karte hain"
  23,77,Albata jab nobat yahan taq poanch jaye gi ke hum inn par sakht azaab ka darwaaza khol den ge to yakayak tum dekho ge ke is haalat mein yeh har kher se mayoos hain
  23,78,woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumhe sُnne aur dekhnay ki quwaten den aur sochnay ko dil diye magar tum log kam hi shukar guzaar hotay ho
  23,79,"wohi hai jis ne tumhe zameen mein phelaya, aur isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
  23,80,wohi zindagi bakhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai gardish Lail o nehar isi ke qabza qudrat mein hai kya tumhari samajh mein yeh baat nahi aati ?
  23,81,magar yeh log wohi kuch kehte hain jo un ke paish ro keh chuke hain
  23,82,"yeh kehte hain"" kya jab hum mar kar matti ho jayen ge aur hadion ka panjar ban kar reh jayen ge to hum ko phir zindah kar ke uthaya jaye ga ?"
  23,83,"hum ne bhi yeh waday bohat sunay hain aur hum se pehlay hamaray baap dada bhi suntay rahay hain yeh mehez afsanaha-ay Parinah hain """
  23,84,"un se kaho, batao agar tum jantay ho, ke yeh zameen aur is ki saari abadi kis ki hai ?"
  23,85,"yeh zaroor kahin ge Allah ki kaho, phir tum hosh mein kyun nahi atay ?"
  23,86,"un se pucho, saton asmano aur arsh azeem ka maalik kon hai ?"
  23,87,"yeh zaroor kahin ge Allah kaho, phir tum drtay kyun nahi ?"
  23,88,"inn se kaho, batao agar tum jantay ho ke har cheez par Iqtidaar kis ka hai? aur kon hai woh jo panah deta hai aur is ke muqablay mein koi panah nahi day sakta ?"
  23,89,"yeh zaroor kahin ge ke yeh baat to Allah hi ke liye hai kaho, phir kahan se tum ko dhoka lagta hai ?"
  23,90,"jo amar haq hai woh hum inn ke samnay le aeye hain, aur koi shak nahi ke yeh log jhutay hain"
  23,91,"Allah ne kisi ko apni aulaad nahi banaya hai aur koi dosra khuda uss ke sath nahi hai agar aisa hota to har khuda apni Khalq ko le kar allag ho jata, aur phir woh aik dosray par charh dorrtay pak hai Allah un baton se jo yeh log banatay hain"
  23,92,"khulay aur chupay ka jan-nay wala, woh balatar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log tajweez kar rahay hain"
  23,93,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, dua karo ke"" parvar-digaar, jis azaab ki inn ko dhamki di ja rahi hai woh agar meri mojoodgi mein to laaye"
  23,94,"to ae mere rab, mujhe un zalim logon mein shaamil nah kejio """
  23,95,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke hum tumhari aankhon ke samnay hi woh cheez le anay ki poori qudrat rakhtay hain jis ki dhamki hum inhen day rahay hain
  23,96,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, buraiee ko is tareeqa se dafaa karo jo behtareen ho jo kuch baatein woh tum par banatay hain woh hamein khoob maloom hain"
  23,97,"aur dua karo ke"" parvar-digaar, mein shyatin ki uksahaton seteri panah mangta hon"
  23,98,"balkay ae mere rab, mein to is se bhi teri panah mangta hon ke woh mere paas ayen """
  23,99,"( yeh log apni karni se baz nah ayen ge ) yahan taq ke jab un mein se kisi ko mout aa jaye gi to kehna shuru kere ga ke"" ae mere rab, mujhe usi duniya mein wapas bhaij degiye jisay mein chore aaya hon"
  23,100,"umeed hai ke ab mein naik amal karoon ga"" hargiz nahi, yeh bas aik baat hai jo woh buk raha hai ab inn sab ( marnay walon ) ke peechay aik barzakh haail hai doosri zindagi ke din taq"
  23,101,"phir jounhi ke sor phoonk diya gaya, un ke darmain phir koi rishta nah rahay ga aur nah woh aik dosray ko poucheen ge"
  23,102,uss waqt jin ke plrhe bhaari hon ge wohi Falah payen ge
  23,103,aur jin ke plrhe halkay hon ge wohi log hon ge jinhon ne apne aap ko ghatay mein daal liya woh jahannum mein hamesha rahen ge
  23,104,aag un ke cheharon ki khaal chaat jaye gi aur unn ke jabray bahar nikal ayen ge
  23,105,""" kya tum wohi log nahi ho ke meri ayaat tumhe sunai jati theen to tum inhen jutlatay thay? """
  23,106,"woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, hamari bad bakhti hum par chhaa gayi thi waqai hum gumraah log thay"
  23,107,"ae parvar-digaar, ab hamein yahan se nikaal day phir hum aisa qasoor karen to zalim hon ge """
  23,108,"Allah taala jawab day ga"" daur ho mere samnay se, parre raho isi mein aur mujh se baat nah karo"
  23,109,"tum wohi log to ho ke mere kuch bande jab kehte thay ke ae hamaray parvar-digaar, hum imaan laaye, hamein maaf kar day, hum par reham kar, Tu sab reahimon se acha Raheem hai"
  23,110,"to tum ne un ka mazaq bana liya yahan taq ke unn ki zid ne tumhe yeh bhi bhula diya ke mein bhi koi hon, aur tum un par hanstay rahay"
  23,111,"aaj unn ke uss sabr ka mein ne yeh phal diya hai ke wohi kamyaab hain """
  23,112,"phir Allah taala un se pouchye ga"" batao, zameen mein tum kitney saal rahay? """
  23,113,"woh kahin ge"" aik din ya din ka bhi kuch hissa hum wahan thire hain shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye """
  23,114,"irshad ho ga"" thori hi der thire ho na, kash tum ne yeh uss waqt jana hota"
  23,115,"kya tum ne yeh samajh rakha tha ke hum ne tumhe fuzool hi peda kya hai aur tumhe hamari taraf kabhi palatna hi nahi hai? """
  23,116,"pas baala o bartar hai Allah , Padasha haqeeqi, koi khuda uss ke siwa nahi, maalik hai arsh buzurag ka"
  23,117,"aur jo koi Allah ke sath kisi aur mabood ko pukare, jis ke liye is ke paas koi Daleel nahi, to is ka hisaab is ke rab ke paas hai aisay kafir kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
  23,118,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho,"" mere rab dar guzar farma, aur reham kar, aur to sab reahimon se acha Raheem hai """
